          <blockquote>
            <h2 style="line-height: 150%; margin-top: 5">
          Raiding Rules and Procedures</h2>
            <p style="line-height: 150%; margin-top: 5">
            <span style="color: black">The Divine Prophecy has various guides 
            and procedures for different raids that can be completed.&nbsp; We 
            strongly encourage all members to visit the
            <a style="color: #3E8AE0; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none; text-line-through: none" href="kb/category.asp">Knowledgebase</a> and review these guides.</span></p>
            <p style="line-height: 150%; margin-top: 5">
            <span style="color: black">To ensure efficient raiding, this page is 
            designed to provide the core basics to all guild-sponsored raids.</span></p>
          </blockquote>
          <table class="MsoNormalTable" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="80%" style="width: 80.0%; border-collapse: collapse; border: medium none; margin-left: .5in" id="AutoNumber3">
            <tr>
              <td width="20%" style="width: 20.0%; border: 1.0pt inset black; padding: .75pt" align="center">
              <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 150%; margin-top: 5"><b>
              <span style="font-size:10.0pt; color:black">
              <a style="color: #3E8AE0; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none; text-line-through: none" href="http://www.divineprophecy.org/Info/raids.asp#Core_Raiding_Rules">Core Raiding Rules</a></span></b></td>
              <td width="20%" style="width: 20.0%; border-left: medium none; border-right: 1.0pt inset black; border-top: 1.0pt inset black; border-bottom: 1.0pt inset black; padding: .75pt" align="center">
              <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 150%; margin-top: 5"><b>
              <span style="font-size:10.0pt; color:black">
              <a style="color: #3E8AE0; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none; text-line-through: none" href="http://www.divineprophecy.org/Info/raids.asp#Loot_Rules">Loot Rules</a></span></b></td>
            </tr>
